outlets.name: Stoned
outlets.about: Stoned is undoubtedly the sexiest thing since all other bars. You'll find all the usuals: great cocktails and plush pasted pinks. It's a ridiculously good spot by Sucat that's breathing some life back into between the Barbican and Shoreditch.
